::Killfest::

Killfest growls, his optics deactivating from the light overload. His 
missle launcher flips over his shoulder and fires two missiles, both 
of them heading toward Angel Prime. The missiles locked on to Angel 
Prime's spark signature, flying toward him at a fast rate.

Killfest activates his jetpack, flying after Angel Prime, though he 
couldn't really see anything yet. But it didn't matter too much. The 
CF was almost on the other side of the planet. This Maximal would 
never get there in time.
